data.description: Convenient location, stylish finishing touches, and inviting layout await you at 939 Westminster in bustling Broome County. Nearly 1800 square feet, this 3 bed 2 bath with a large fenced in backyard offers privacy and functionality to utilize your new outdoor space. Store your equipment or belongings for the seasons in a large out building, or in your detached one car garage. When the cold Upstate NY months come calling, retire to your new large living room area with an open concept into an updated kitchen to host your house warming party. This property also boasts a first floor bedroom and full bath for added convenience. A beautiful separate large dining room is another added feature to this lovely home. Call today for your private showing.
